Waterfall
===========

SMS --> School Management System

100 years back --> Final exam

stakeholders
============
Teachers -> Not serious to complete syllabus from DAY-1
Parents -> Yes. Worried about whether they pass or not
Students -> Not serious to study from DAY-1

30%

Process Change
============
UNIT TEST-I, II, III, IV
Q, H, PRE-FINAL, Final

