Honda City


Waterfall --> 10 times testing --> 100
Agile --> 30 times testing --> 101
DevOps --> 100 times --> 102

Agile is part of DevOps
============
Modules --> Signup, Login, Menu, Order, Shipping, Delivery, Payments

Signup
========
1 month
DAY-1 --> 100 lines of code --> enter your first name, enter your last name
deploy this 100 lines --> test this 100 lines

3 defects --> Co-operation, Co-ordination, Collobaration between teams

DAY-10 --> We should deploy and test everything.

DevOps is a process of building, testing and releasing code on the same day when developer writes something. through this process we can acheive colloboration between teams, faster releases and less defects

Speed and Accuracy

